  "texts": [
    "By employing the distilled model as a filter, we achieved an average attack success rate of 49.8% using the Syntax tree-based method, and 58.3% with the LLM-based method.",
    "This method significantly improved effectiveness.",
    "Our research evaluated the effectiveness of DistillSeq on a range of LLMs including GPT-3.5, GPT-4.0, Vicuna-13B, and Llama-13B.",
    "In scenarios where DistillSeq was not employed, the attack success rates were recorded as 31.5% for GPT-3.5, 21.4% for GPT-4.0, 28.3% for Vicuna-13B, and 30.9% for Llama-13B.",
    "Remarkably, with the implementation of DistillSeq, these success rates significantly increased to 58.5%, 50.7%, 52.5%, and 54.4% for each model, respectively."
  ],
